## Phase 4: Production Verification

### 4.1 Build Verification
```bash
# Ensure no build errors
npm run build

# Check for unused CSS variables
npm run lint
```

### 4.2 Runtime Testing
1. Start dev server: `npm run dev`
2. Toggle theme in UI (if theme switcher exists)
3. Navigate through:
   - Executive Cockpit
   - Projects Ledger
   - Tender Kanban
   - Any form interfaces

### 4.3 Browser Testing
Test in:
- Chrome (latest)
- Safari (if on Mac)
- Edge (Windows)

