## Quick Reference: Design Tokens

| Token | Light Mode Value | Usage |
|-------|------------------|-------|
| `--bg-layer` | `hsl(40, 25%, 96%)` | Main background |
| `--bg-surface` | `hsl(0, 0%, 100%)` | Card surfaces |
| `--bg-hover` | `hsl(40, 18%, 92%)` | Hover states |
| `--text-primary` | `hsl(210, 40%, 16%)` | Body text |
| `--text-secondary` | `hsl(215, 20%, 35%)` | Secondary text |
| `--text-tertiary` | `hsl(215, 15%, 42%)` | Muted text |
| `--morgan-teal` | `hsl(184, 35%, 48%)` | Brand accent |
| `--surface-border` | `hsla(210, 29%, 24%, 0.1)` | Subtle borders |
| `--color-critical` | `hsl(355, 78%, 42%)` | Error/critical |

---

## Troubleshooting

### Issue: Text is too light in light mode
**Solution**: Replace `text-zinc-400` with `text-[var(--text-secondary)]`

### Issue: Borders are invisible
**Solution**: Use `border-[var(--surface-border)]` instead of `border-white/5`

### Issue: Teal looks blue
**Solution**: Replace `text-emerald-500` with `text-[var(--morgan-teal)]`

### Issue: Cards have no depth
**Solution**: Add `shadow-sm hover:shadow-md` to card containers

